MERRILL A. YARBROUGH and CHARLES P. CARSON, v. H. LESLIE QUIGG, as Chief of Police of the City of Miami, Florida. 18 So. (2nd) 477

June Term, 1944

June 23, 1944 Special Division B ,On Rehearing Aug. 1st, 1944 Ernest E. Roberts, for appellants. J. W. Watson, Jr., for appellee. PER CURIAM:

Order and decree appealed from reversed on authority of the case of State ex rel. Wilson v. Quigg, 154 Fla. 448, 17 So. (2nd) 697.

BUFORD, C. J., BROWN, CHAPMAN and THOMAS, JJ., concur.
